                                    <h1 class="position-relative">Product Testing</h1>
                                </div>
                                <p class="fst-italic mt-5 fs-3">
                                    We deliver products which are robust and safe, and perform
                                    well under the rigours of anticipated use and misuse.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Meeting statutory regulation and compliance is essential,
                                    however understanding and ensuring the product performs well
                                    under the rigours of use and application is key to maintaining
                                    consumer confidence in the product and the brand. Often a
                                    specific standard can be interpreted in different ways, and
                                    our design team will work closely with the test house to
                                    ensure the outcome is successful.
                                </p>
